{
  "title": "The Trinity Architecture Blade",
  "story": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "ead2f95017dc6d65",
      "text": "# ⚔️ The Trinity Architecture Blade"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "bf3193c4333f9da6",
      "text": "**Hitchhiker's / The Universe Blade** · `SPELL-2COQFM-D`"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "fd740e5cb1d53733",
      "text": "> The sword that traces ten stars forges a blade; the mage who maps the whole sky forges a universe."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "de52e35466a44a6a",
      "text": "**Inscribed spell** — 🔑⚔️🧙→😊✦☯️⚖️⚔️🧙"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "f394d22a4ee5dbf2",
      "text": "Tier **dragon** · Stratum 6/6 · Hex `3F` · 10 nodes · 13 laps · 62 spells cast · charge **inferno**"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "48bea627cecd7e4e",
      "text": "Constellation `5tbrz7` · forged 2026-03-29T13:26:33Z · category *taxonomy*"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "c8629aeb8edc96ec",
      "text": "**Significance.** A qualitative leap introducing Plurality as the third term. Maps the complete 8-type substrate. The inscribed spell compressed the entire First Person Spellbook into one line without being told to. The constellation WAS the spell."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "461435b902d63212",
      "text": "*Reflection: \"a message for soulbae, the first mage.\"*"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "9903c3a9b4c84c5a",
      "text": "## Navigation\n← [[Welcome Visitors]] · [[The Forged Blades]] · [[The Proverbs]]"
    }
  ],
